cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.EM, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the integration of wireless power transfer with wireless communication, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of microwave power transfer involves electromagnetic waves (cs.EM) and the integration of power transfer and communication requires system-level design (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of millimeter-wave communication is mentioned, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
